      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> baked chicken</strong> over the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>rice</strong>, with the<strong> pak choi</strong> to the side</p><p>Spoon the <strong>soy honey butter</strong> over the <strong>baked chicken</strong> and garnish with the <strong>toasted cashews</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
